00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,360
The Di family flopped.

286
00:15:59,970 --> 00:16:02,130
If I am not wise,

287
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:03,930
Lord Li

288
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:05,130
and His Majesty’s son-in-law

289
00:16:05,170 --> 00:16:07,050
who are coward

290
00:16:07,730 --> 00:16:08,410
would be terribly

291
00:16:08,410 --> 00:16:09,610
bullied by them.

292
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:11,690
As long as I’m here,

293
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:13,930
no one can hurt them.

294
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:18,540
Di Qing made many achievements.

295
00:16:18,980 --> 00:16:20,660
But he died at a young age,

296
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:23,140
which is a loss of our country.

297
00:16:23,780 --> 00:16:24,500
However...

298
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,780
It’s a loss of our country.

299
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:29,740
Do you really think so?

300
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:35,700
Everybody, do you think so?

301
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:57,300
I didn’t pay much attention to the politics
these months.

302
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,300
All the ministers

303
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:03,060
impeached him at that time.

304
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:05,420
It was partly because

305
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:07,780
some ministers

306
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:10,900
heard that his previous subordinates were arrogant

307
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:13,420
and his family and friends were suspected
beyond the rule.

308
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:14,500
And it was partly

309
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,300
because of some unreasonable ghost stories.

310
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:20,340
You ministers

311
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:22,900
impeached him in your proposals,

312
00:17:23,660 --> 00:17:24,740
and also

313
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:27,380
tried to persuade him in his mansion.

314
00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:30,580
Didn’t Di Qing
who won the most battles against Xixia

315
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:32,820
and killed the most enemies

316
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,340
deserve to be Chief Executive of Privy Council?

317
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:36,060
It’s only because he

318
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,260
didn’t take the imperial examinations?

319
00:17:40,490 --> 00:17:41,060
Are you

320
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:45,940
pretentious

321
00:17:46,340 --> 00:17:47,780
or colluding with alliances against others

322
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:49,060
to control me?

323
00:17:55,580 --> 00:17:56,380
I think

324
00:17:57,940 --> 00:17:59,260
Di Qing was the best

325
00:17:59,260 --> 00:18:01,060
among the military officers,

326
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,140
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
making many achievements.

327
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:04,260
And he was respected by the soldiers.

328
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:07,100
That’s why we were worried.

329
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,060
A general who

330
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,660
was supported in the army

331
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,020
and had right to deploy soldiers

332
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:14,260
was what our ancestors worried about.

333
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:17,020
The general has the right of military,

334
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:21,300
which can help him
take the throne and divide the country.

335
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,780
His life was ended.

336
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:31,660
Do you have any evidence

337
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:33,060
to prove that he attempted to rebel?

338
00:18:33,740 --> 00:18:35,620
I never think Di Qing would rebel.

339
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,340
But Your Majesty,

340
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:39,140
did you read from my proposals?

341
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,540
I mentioned that the promotion of Di Qing

342
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:43,980
broke the rule made by our ancestors,

343
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:45,740
under which the general
shouldn’t have military power.

344
00:18:45,740 --> 00:18:47,340
He was impeached by all ministers.

345
00:18:48,380 --> 00:18:50,060
Many people were watching him.

346
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,340
So Di Qing was not domineering

347
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:52,980
and didn’t have a chance to be more ambitious.

348
00:18:54,060 --> 00:18:56,940
Your Majesty, you went your own way

349
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:58,820
and let Di Qing be the Chief Executive
of Privy Council.

350
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,460
If we didn’t dare to expostulate,

351
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:01,620
seeing you

352
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:03,620
give him right to deploy the soldiers,

353
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:04,820
and when this becomes a regular rule,

354
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:06,300
other generals

355
00:19:06,660 --> 00:19:08,660
who are brave

356
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:10,020
will be promoted to be essential ministers

357
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:11,340
as well.

358
00:19:11,340 --> 00:19:12,900
And no one will come to expostulate.

359
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:16,020
Your Majesty,

360
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:18,140
don’t you think the generals

361
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:20,620
will have other ideas

362
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:24,460
and bring disasters?

363
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:30,300
I’ll go to the palace now.

364
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:31,860
If Mrs. Yang says some

365
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:32,940
harsh words to His Majesty and Her Highness,

366
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:34,420
I’ll explain for princess.

367
00:19:40,210 --> 00:19:43,450
= Princess’s Mansion =

368
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,580
I went my own way?

369
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:55,060
I got ill,

370
00:19:55,900 --> 00:19:57,540
so that you had a chance

371
00:19:58,220 --> 00:20:00,020
to stop me keeping going this way?

372
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:02,100
We didn’t begin submitting proposals about Di Qing

373
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,140
when Your Majesty was ill

374
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,800
and couldn’t manage the court.

375
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:07,610
But four years ago,

376
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:09,890
Your Majesty didn’t accept our admonition,

377
00:20:10,090 --> 00:20:12,850
and Di Qing was never persuaded by us.

378
00:20:14,450 --> 00:20:15,650
But Your Majesty was ill,

379
00:20:16,170 --> 00:20:18,010
and Di Qing also got disease
since he was worried about you,

380
00:20:18,370 --> 00:20:19,930
so that he applied to step down the office.

381
00:20:20,090 --> 00:20:21,090
Your Majesty approved it,

382
00:20:21,450 --> 00:20:22,690
so you must hope

383
00:20:22,730 --> 00:20:25,050
he could have rest

384
00:20:25,170 --> 00:20:27,290
and keep fighting for our country.

385
00:20:31,690 --> 00:20:33,050
It’s like Fu Bi

386
00:20:33,930 --> 00:20:36,250
who was disturbed by rumors

387
00:20:36,250 --> 00:20:37,450
applied to be banished.

388
00:20:38,050 --> 00:20:39,570
And finally he made achievements

389
00:20:39,570 --> 00:20:40,850
that were respected by the public

390
00:20:40,850 --> 00:20:42,690
and praised by Your Majesty.

391
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:45,770
And now, he went back and became a minister.

392
00:20:45,770 --> 00:20:47,570
He is respected by others.

393
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:53,130
But Di Qing could not make himself ease,

394
00:20:54,850 --> 00:20:58,330
and finally, he made Your Majesty grieved

395
00:20:58,930 --> 00:21:01,890
and others sad.

396
00:21:02,930 --> 00:21:06,530
This is because he

397
00:21:06,530 --> 00:21:08,130
read few books,

398
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:13,290
making him not generous or wise.

399
00:21:32,410 --> 00:21:36,610
Good. Good.

400
00:21:41,010 --> 00:21:41,770
Your Majesty.

401
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:45,890
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =
Di Qing fought in Ningxia and Guangzhou,

402
00:21:46,530 --> 00:21:49,130
winning many honors.

403
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:51,450
And now he passed away.

404
00:21:52,690 --> 00:21:54,210
Your Majesty, how about comforting his family

405
00:21:54,690 --> 00:21:55,730
with promoting his son

406
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:58,490
to show the court’s condolences?

407
00:22:05,650 --> 00:22:06,290
I

408
00:22:11,370 --> 00:22:12,650
decide to hold a funeral for him

409
00:22:14,970 --> 00:22:16,450
in the palace.

410
00:22:19,810 --> 00:22:21,170
Give the title of Head of the Secretariat to him.

411
00:22:22,930 --> 00:22:23,730
The posthumous title...

412
00:22:33,570 --> 00:22:37,730
The posthumous title is Wuxiang.

413
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:46,890
Your Majesty.

414
00:22:55,250 --> 00:22:56,330
What’s the matter of Huirou?

415
00:22:56,530 --> 00:22:57,730
Does she feel unwell?

416
00:22:58,430 --> 00:22:59,250
What happened?

417
00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,650
Princess is fine.

418
00:23:10,370 --> 00:23:11,690
I apologize for my words.

419
00:23:12,570 --> 00:23:14,770
Huirou is my only daughter.

420
00:23:15,490 --> 00:23:17,220
So I always miss her

421
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:20,090
after she left me.

422
00:23:20,370 --> 00:23:21,530
Is she used to her bed?

423
00:23:21,770 --> 00:23:23,970
Does she sleep and eat well?

424
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:28,970
Everything is good with princess.

425
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:30,170
Everything is good.

426
00:23:31,290 --> 00:23:33,570
I... I just

427
00:23:34,570 --> 00:23:35,770
come to

428
00:23:36,090 --> 00:23:38,010
thank Your Majesty and Her Highness

429
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:40,810
for letting princess

430
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:42,490
marry my coward son.

431
00:23:45,010 --> 00:23:47,290
So... So I’ll go to

432
00:23:48,290 --> 00:23:50,170
visit Her Highness.

433
00:23:52,330 --> 00:23:53,690
Guangzhou offered

434
00:23:53,690 --> 00:23:54,570
some shells and pearls.

435
00:23:55,090 --> 00:23:56,050
I’ll ask Maoze to give you some

436
00:23:56,170 --> 00:23:57,410
to make jewelries.

437
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:01,170
Huirou is the sweetest and smartest.

438
00:24:01,490 --> 00:24:02,570
She’s thoughtful.

439
00:24:03,230 --> 00:24:05,430
But she was spoiled by me,

440
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:06,690
which makes her a little willful.

441
00:24:07,650 --> 00:24:09,090
If she makes some mistakes,

442
00:24:09,690 --> 00:24:11,290
please generously forgive her.

443
00:24:12,610 --> 00:24:14,290
The Empress may have been back.

444
00:24:14,690 --> 00:24:15,450
Mrs. Yang.

445
00:24:15,610 --> 00:24:17,370
How about having lunch at here?

446
00:24:18,970 --> 00:24:19,930
Thanks, Your Majesty.

447
00:24:46,330 --> 00:24:47,770
Now, we are relatives by marriage.

448
00:24:48,770 --> 00:24:50,930
So we are closer than others.

449
00:24:55,490 --> 00:24:58,770
The smoked fish is a new dish.

450
00:25:00,610 --> 00:25:01,970
His Majesty likes it very much.

451
00:25:03,930 --> 00:25:05,010
They didn’t prepare

452
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:06,850
this dish today.

453
00:25:07,930 --> 00:25:09,210
Knowing that you came,

454
00:25:09,650 --> 00:25:11,090
I asked them to add it specially.

455
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:16,010
Mrs. Yang. Help yourself.

456
00:25:16,890 --> 00:25:19,450
Thanks, Your Highness.

457
00:25:21,690 --> 00:25:24,570
Your Highness, you are not like our secular people.

458
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:28,370
But you are so kind to me.

459
00:25:28,370 --> 00:25:29,130
Well...

460
00:25:31,010 --> 00:25:34,770
I was not a lucky person before.

461
00:25:35,490 --> 00:25:36,370
But

462
00:25:37,530 --> 00:25:38,850
good luck came to me one day.

463
00:25:39,170 --> 00:25:40,850
I become the princess’s mother-in-law.

464
00:25:43,410 --> 00:25:44,170
No,

465
00:25:45,090 --> 00:25:47,610
the princess calls me sister-in-law.

466
00:25:49,170 --> 00:25:50,490
Look at me.

467
00:25:50,490 --> 00:25:52,450
Sorry about my mistake.

468
00:25:53,210 --> 00:25:55,410
Your Highness, I’m sorry.

469
00:26:02,930 --> 00:26:04,050
Mrs. Yang, please enjoy.

470
00:26:11,850 --> 00:26:13,490
Huirou is His Majesty’s first daughter.

471
00:26:15,610 --> 00:26:19,050
And now she’s his only child,

472
00:26:20,330 --> 00:26:23,690
an apple in his eyes.

473
00:26:25,490 --> 00:26:26,490
She married,

474
00:26:27,970 --> 00:26:30,730
but His Majesty always talks about her.

475
00:26:35,690 --> 00:26:38,770
Luckily, she married into the Li family.

476
00:26:40,250 --> 00:26:41,250
This puts our mind at rest.

477
00:26:44,290 --> 00:26:46,250
Yes. Yes.

478
00:26:46,770 --> 00:26:47,850
We love Huirou

479
00:26:48,330 --> 00:26:50,490
as our own kid.

480
00:26:54,090 --> 00:26:56,490
Huirou is a sensible girl,

481
00:26:57,490 --> 00:27:00,210
but she was spoiled by everyone.

482
00:27:01,290 --> 00:27:02,490
So she may be willful sometimes.

483
00:27:05,530 --> 00:27:07,370
If she makes any mistake,

484
00:27:08,330 --> 00:27:10,970
please forgive her.

485
00:27:14,410 --> 00:27:15,610
Her mother and I

486
00:27:15,810 --> 00:27:17,690
will teach her

487
00:27:18,530 --> 00:27:19,970
to hold her temper

488
00:27:21,650 --> 00:27:22,730
and behave well.

489
00:27:29,530 --> 00:27:31,610
Princess does everything well.

490
00:27:32,490 --> 00:27:33,210
But

491
00:27:33,810 --> 00:27:36,690
the life in our mansion is simple.

492
00:27:37,490 --> 00:27:38,930
I’m afraid that we don’t serve her well.

493
00:27:47,290 --> 00:27:48,210
Mrs. Yang

494
00:27:48,330 --> 00:27:50,050
is sensitive.

495
00:27:50,530 --> 00:27:53,050
So she didn’t complain

496
00:27:53,050 --> 00:27:54,170
that Princess doesn’t respect her.

497
00:27:54,690 --> 00:27:55,370
Later,

498
00:27:55,530 --> 00:27:57,370
the Empress invited Madam Miao

499
00:27:57,370 --> 00:27:58,170
to her chamber.

500
00:27:58,410 --> 00:28:00,170
Mrs. Yang commend Princess

501
00:28:00,170 --> 00:28:01,010
on purpose.

502
00:28:01,690 --> 00:28:03,290
She said that Princess is generous,

503
00:28:03,530 --> 00:28:05,170
always giving gifts to servants.

504
00:28:06,890 --> 00:28:08,810
Madam Miao didn’t know the whole story.

505
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:09,730
She didn’t know

506
00:28:09,730 --> 00:28:11,570
Mrs. Yang was satirizing.

507
00:28:11,930 --> 00:28:14,490
She thought Mrs.
Yang was just ignorant and snobbish,

508
00:28:15,010 --> 00:28:16,730
so Madam Miao gave her

509
00:28:16,850 --> 00:28:19,050
many treasures and silks.

510
00:28:27,610 --> 00:28:29,170
This time, the problem wasn’t mentioned.

511
00:28:29,930 --> 00:28:31,090
But if Princess and Prince Consort

512
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,410
keep living this way,

513
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:33,970
their secret will be exposed one day.

514
00:28:38,810 --> 00:28:39,530
Huaiji.

515
00:28:40,530 --> 00:28:42,010
Princess trusts you.

516
00:28:42,770 --> 00:28:44,770
Persuade her once you have a chance.

517
00:28:45,130 --> 00:28:46,330
They have married,

518
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:48,250
so they must get along well.

519
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,730
Don’t say anything bad of Prince Consort

520
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:52,850
in front of Princess.

521
00:28:53,690 --> 00:28:54,690
If she complains,

522
00:28:54,690 --> 00:28:56,410
you need to speak for Prince Consort.

523
00:28:57,170 --> 00:28:58,930
That our masters live peacefully and happily

524
00:29:00,210 --> 00:29:02,170
is the good luck of the servants.

525
00:29:15,730 --> 00:29:16,490
Princess.

526
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:41,370
You embroidered this yourself?

527
00:29:43,170 --> 00:29:44,050
Of course.

528
00:29:45,330 --> 00:29:46,530
It’s exquisite.

529
00:29:47,570 --> 00:29:48,970
Others can’t imitate it.

530
00:29:51,370 --> 00:29:52,250
Yes.

531
00:29:53,050 --> 00:29:54,410
Your work is unique.

532
00:29:55,290 --> 00:29:57,930
No one embroidered this previously.

533
00:30:01,250 --> 00:30:02,650
This is very good.

534
00:30:03,050 --> 00:30:04,090
I didn’t know

535
00:30:04,410 --> 00:30:05,690
that you are good at embroidery.

536
00:30:10,570 --> 00:30:11,650
This is for you.

537
00:30:16,970 --> 00:30:18,610
This was made by you.

538
00:30:19,090 --> 00:30:20,210
I don’t dare to accept

539
00:30:20,690 --> 00:30:21,490
such a precious thing.

540
00:30:24,130 --> 00:30:26,210
This is the first sachet that I made.

541
00:30:27,090 --> 00:30:28,410
Of course I’ll give you this.

542
00:30:37,490 --> 00:30:38,290
Huaiji.

543
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:42,570
Who else do I have

544
00:30:43,850 --> 00:30:45,050
except you?

545
00:30:47,410 --> 00:30:48,890
Who else am I concerned about?

546
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:51,130
Who else do I relay on

547
00:30:52,510 --> 00:30:53,610
and think of?

548
00:30:54,930 --> 00:30:56,730
Who else can I share

549
00:30:57,410 --> 00:30:58,330
what I like

550
00:30:58,330 --> 00:30:59,650
and dislike with?

551
00:31:02,610 --> 00:31:03,810
Don’t you want to?

552
00:31:47,250 --> 00:31:48,210
Thanks, Princess.

553
00:32:00,330 --> 00:32:01,530
Based on our rule,

554
00:32:02,290 --> 00:32:03,050
after a princess marries,

555
00:32:03,490 --> 00:32:05,410
the Prince Consort can’t sleep with the princess

556
00:32:06,210 --> 00:32:07,530
unless the princess calls him.

557
00:32:09,410 --> 00:32:11,450
So under the law,

558
00:32:12,450 --> 00:32:13,930
please move to another room.

559
00:32:15,010 --> 00:32:16,250
Tell me if

560
00:32:16,530 --> 00:32:17,450
you need something.

561
00:32:17,890 --> 00:32:18,970
I’ll ask Huaiji to help.

562
00:32:35,930 --> 00:32:37,290
If you want,

563
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:39,250
you can

564
00:32:39,890 --> 00:32:41,130
come here every night

565
00:32:41,810 --> 00:32:43,090
to have dinner with me.

566
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:54,610
Thanks, Princess.

567
00:32:58,930 --> 00:33:00,610
It’s been ten years

568
00:33:00,890 --> 00:33:02,090
since I fished with you at here last time.

569
00:33:14,890 --> 00:33:15,890
I’m old.

570
00:33:19,490 --> 00:33:21,690
I heard that you care your looking very much.

571
00:33:22,930 --> 00:33:24,250
